Package: ASCATCATA
Type: Package
Title: Functionalities for applying ANOVA simultaneous components analysis on Temporal Check All That Apply Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Michele", "Ricci", email = "ricci.michele94@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Michele Ricci <ricci.michele94@gmail.com>
Description: A set of function to apply ANOVA simultaneous component analysis on Temporal Check All That Apply data. It contains a set of function to apply the analysis on a TCATA dataset in long format table and to represent the results in biplots. It contains also a function to apply a permutation test to validate the analysis.
depends: R (>= 4.0.0),
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
